Author: Asteria Nocturna
Name: Divination.AetheryteLinkInChat
Punchline: Quick teleport for mob hunts and treasure hunts!
Description: Display a teleport link to the nearest aetherite for the map link from the in-game chat. Type /alic to configure the plugin.
Changelog:
646ef3c: Merge branch 'master' of ssh://github.com/SlashNephy/Divination
1b5706f: Merge pull request #649 from Uriei/master

Ignore text inside map link when looking for world name
bc149dc: include oceania DC option
e39f14a: Ignore text inside map link when looking for world name

This was causing issue with maps like Ultima Thule, detecting it was always in the Ultima japan world.
80f87e4: wait before world traveling
2ab3131: allow DC traveling
683f6ee: more delay
d86b4b3: delay before continue
011fc46: Update issue templates
f6d39b4: Merge pull request #646 from SlashNephy/chore/spawn-location-spawn-release-actions

support spawn_location / spawn_release actions for early access users
a5c7aee: Merge pull request #647 from SlashNephy/feat/lifestream-integration

AetheryteLinkInChat: Lifestream integration
dda5d7c: check Lifestream availability
d92c3dd: cancel handling
1b34ff3: teleport with Lifestream
5809f48: LifestreamPayload
dd37254: CombinedAetherytePayload
72942b3: move
1bec4b1: add option
6bfd3a4: support spawn_location / spawn_release actions for early access users
bc2df78: zonePoiIds may be null
2d2ba6d: const event types
e2c6259: too long
d44a3de: queue /teleportgc as well
41fdc58: consider zone instance for spawn histories
cb0c43d: apply format
220db53: use collection literal
281e177: remove unused fields
386f1d2: append MapLink only if pop location is known

Early access payload may not contain ZonePoiIds
f66fc02: adjust simplified reports setting
033e44f: Rank A/B mobs are not supported in Faloop
